FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Kuwait said its air
OL,7,Fdefences had opened fire early on
OL,8,FMonday morning to intercept incoming
OL,9,Fdrone and missile fire, as Iran
OL,10,Facknowledged launching a retaliatory
OL,11,Fstrike.
OL,13,FThe duelling attacks reflect the
OL,14,Ffragility of a weekslong ceasefire in
OL,15,Fthe Iran war, which has seen repeated
OL,16,Fattacks even as American and Iranian
OL,17,Fofficials try to negotiate a deal to
OL,18,Fextend it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,F"US fighter aircraft swiftly responded
OL,7,Fby eliminating Iranian air defences, a
OL,8,Fground control station, and two one-
OL,9,Fway attack drones that posed clear
OL,10,Fthreats to ships transiting regional
OL,11,Fwaters," Central Command said.
OL,13,FThe US military said no American
OL,14,Ftroops were hurt in the attacks.
OL,16,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,17,FGuard said in a statement carried by
OL,18,Fthe state-run IRNA news agency that US
OL,19,Fforces had targeted a
OL,20,Ftelecommunications tower on Iran's
OL,21,FSirik Island.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
