CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FThe Guard said it responded with an
OL,7,Fattack on the US air base used to
OL,8,Flaunch that attack without saying
OL,9,Fwhere, likely referring to the attack
OL,10,Fon Kuwait. The country is home to US
OL,11,FArmy Central, the military's Mideast
OL,12,Fforward command.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
