OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FIranian state television later shared
OL,7,Ffootage of the ballistic missile
OL,8,Flaunch, including a close-up showing a
OL,9,Fsticker on its body depicting a
OL,10,Fbruised US President Donald Trump
OL,11,Foverlaid on a "closed" Strait of
OL,12,FHormuz with the caption: "Until the
OL,13,Flast American soldier leaves the
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,16,FIran has maintained its chokehold on
OL,17,Fthe Strait of Hormuz in the meantime,
OL,18,Fdisrupting global energy supplies as a
OL,19,Ffifth of all oil and natural gas
OL,20,Ftraded once passed through the narrow
OL,21,Fmouth of the Persian Gulf.
OL,26,@sD@OOUsD@VO]tD@ZOU
