OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FMeanwhile, fighting continues to
OL,7,Fescalate as Israel extends its
OL,8,Foccupation of Lebanon beyond the
OL,9,FLitani River and as the militant group
OL,10,FHezbollah continues to launch drones
OL,11,Finto Israel.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FAttacks rattle ceasefire talks
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
