PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FThe attacks represent the latest
OL,7,Fescalation between the US and Iran,
OL,8,Feven as both have insisted they are
OL,9,Fcontinuing to negotiate, particularly
OL,10,Fover Iran's stockpile of highly
OL,11,Fenriched uranium.
OL,13,FOver the weekend, the US fired a
OL,14,Fmissile into the engine room of a
OL,15,FGambia-flagged cargo ship trying to
OL,16,Fbreak its blockade of Iranian ports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
