PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FA trickle of ships made it out of the
OL,7,Fstrait, but pressure continues on
OL,8,Fglobal energy supplies, as well as
OL,9,Fchemical fertiliser, which has led to
OL,10,Ffears of food shortages.
OL,12,FThe Gulf region produces 30% of
OL,13,Fglobally traded chemical fertilisers.
OL,15,FTrump met with advisers on Friday but
OL,16,Fhas yet to decide on whether to move
OL,17,Fahead with a deal to extend the
OL,18,Fceasefire and reopen the strait.
OL,20,FIran has said the deal had not been
OL,21,Ffinalised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
