PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780319468
OL,3,CUS bombs Iranian military sites as
OL,4,CIran launches strikes in Gulf
OL,6,FTrump expressed optimism about the
OL,7,Ftalks in a post on his Truth Social
OL,8,Fplatform early Monday in Washington,
OL,9,Fmocking critics without addressing the
OL,10,Fongoing crossfire.
OL,12,F"Iran really wants to make a deal, and
OL,13,Fit will be a good one for the U.S.A.
OL,14,Fand those that are with us," he wrote.
OL,15,F"Just sit back and relax, it will all
OL,16,Fwork out well in the end ` It always
OL,17,Fdoes!"
